cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.MA, cs.SY, cs.AI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper focuses on using fiducial markers in field robotics applications, specifically for swarm autonomous robotic boats. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision): The paper proposes a novel methodology for improving pose estimation accuracy of fiducial markers using RGB sensors. 
- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems): The paper discusses the use of fiducial markers for indirect communication in swarm robotics. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper presents experimental results of applying the proposed methodology to create robotic formations. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses computer vision techniques to improve the accuracy of pose estimation in robotic applications.
